data.title: Dive into anything
data.text:
Tell us if you know the etymology or meaning of commonly used words in area / locality names.

Are these correct?

Gutta = rock (eg. Panjagutta), Bowli = stepped water well (eg. Gachibowli), Konda = hill (eg. Kondapur), Cheruvu = lake, Kunta = pond? (eg. Kudikunta lake), Banda = dam? (eg. Masjid Banda), Betta = ?

Please share more names.
